Controls:

Keyboard:
    WASD/Arrow Keys - Move/Target Direction
    Space - Hold to place pipe in Direction
    Shift - Hold to remove pipe in Direction
    Q - Rotate Left
    E - Rotate Right

Controller (XBox Layout):
    Left Analog/D-Pad - Move/Target Direction
    A - Hold to place pipe in Direction
    Y - Hold to remove pipe in Direction
    Left Bumper - Rotate Left
    Right Bumper - Rotate Right